    <item>
      <title>Adobe 股价因全年预测疲软而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-13/adobe-shares-fall-on-weak-full-year-forecast-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adobe 股价在盘后交易中大幅下跌，此前这家软件公司给出的全年预测在关键指标上弱于预期。它还报告了第四季度业绩。彭博资讯的阿努拉格·拉纳 (Anurag Rana) 讨论了结果。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-13/adobe-shares-fall-on-weak-full-year-forecast-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 21:38:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着降息押注的增加，道指创下近两年来的首个纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/dow-hits-first-record-in-nearly-two-years-as-rate-cut-bets-build</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道琼斯工业平均指数创下近两年来首次收盘纪录，收复了美联储为抑制通胀而大幅加息造成的所有损失，华尔街信心增强，认为美联储已经不再提高借贷成本，并准备开始削减利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/dow-hits-first-record-in-nearly-two-years-as-rate-cut-bets-build</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 21:18:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第三位维权投资者敦促三星物产做出改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/samsung-c-t-is-said-to-be-pushed-for-changes-by-third-activist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在另外两名投资者公开批评后，三星物产股东 Whitebox Advisors 正在向这家韩国企业集团施压，要求其采取明确的资本配置计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/samsung-c-t-is-said-to-be-pushed-for-changes-by-third-activist</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储考虑 2024 年降息，美元一个月来跌幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/dollar-drops-1-against-select-g-10-peers-as-fed-mulls-2024-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储维持基准利率不变并提出 2024 年货币宽松政策的更激进预测后，美元正经历一个月来最糟糕的一天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/dollar-drops-1-against-select-g-10-peers-as-fed-mulls-2024-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 20:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美联储降息，美国国债大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/traders-add-to-bet-on-interest-rate-cuts-in-2024-on-fed-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，美国国债市场出现了自 3 月份几家地区性银行破产以来的最大单日涨幅，交易员们接受了美联储结束加息的信号，加大了对 2024 年更大幅度降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/traders-add-to-bet-on-interest-rate-cuts-in-2024-on-fed-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 19:14:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鸽派美联储暗示收益率下降，标普 500 指数突破 4,700 点：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储的鸽派信号推动标准普尔 500 指数逼近历史高点，同时债券收益率下降，华尔街的跨资产反弹得到了额外的鼓励。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 22:31:35 GMT</pubDate>
